Inventory List:
===============

1.  README - This file.

2.  Directory Euler/bin/ - contains compiled class files for:
            a. org.luciter.euler.Problem67 -
                The class file containing the solution for /Poject/Euler Problem 67 
            b. org.luciter.euler.Problem67Test -
                Groovy test cases for org.luciter.euler.Problem67
                
3.  Directory Euler/lib/ - contains jar files employ by:
            a. org.luciter.euler.Problem67
            b. org.luciter.euler.Problem67Test
            
4.  Directory Euler/src/ - contains source file org.luciter.euler.Problem67.groovy

5.  Directory Euler/test/ - contains source files org.luciter.euler.Problem67Test.groovy

6.  Directory Euler/test_files/ - contains test files
            a. bad_alpha_char.txt - detects non-numeric character and aborts.
                Expected abortion message sample:
                
                In file name::./test_files/bad_alpha_char.txt
                Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: An input value 'a' is *NOT* numeric.  Task aborted!

            b. bad_larger_first_line.txt - detects first line too long.
                Expected abortion message sample:
                
                In file name::./test_files/bad_larger_first_line.txt
                Exception in thread "main" java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Prior entry length::0 Current input line length::8.  They should be incrementing one by one.

            c. bad_multiple_blank_lines.txt - detects multiple blank lines and aborts.
                Expected abortion message sample:
                
                In file name::./test_files/bad_multiple_blank_lines.txt
                Exception in thread "main" java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Prior entry length::3 Current input line length::1.  They should be incrementing one by one.

            d. bad_alpha_char.txt - detects non-numeric character and aborts.
                Expected abortion message sample:
                
                In file name::./test_files/bad_alpha_char.txt
                Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: An input value '$' is *NOT* numeric.  Task aborted!

            e. bad_zero_length.txt - detects non-numeric character and aborts.
                Expected abortion message sample:
                
                In file name::./test_files/bad_zero_length.txt
                Exception in thread "main" java.lang.IllegalStateException: File is empty; aborting ...

            f. bad_row_sequence.txt - file rows are expected to be incrementing one by one.
                Expected abortion message sample:
                
                In file name::./test_files/bad_row_sequence.txt
                Exception in thread "main" java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Prior entry length::4 Current input line length::3.  They should be incrementing one by one.

            g. triangler_euler.txt - 100 rows test file from Project Euler.
