Usage (Unix):
=============

  After unzipping the Euler.zip, change directory to Euler (cd Euler).
  
  To execute problem solver:
    java -cp lib/*:bin:. org.luciter.euler.Problem67 <File Name>
    
    e.g.
    java -cp lib/*:bin:. org.luciter.euler.Problem67 ./test_files/triangle_test_100rows.txt

  To execute problem solver junit tester:
    java -cp lib/*:bin:. org.junit.runner.JUnitCore org.luciter.euler.Problem67Test
    



